items.name: Nygglatho Astartus/ナイグラート・アスタルトス (Shuumatsu Nani Shitemasu ka? Isogashii desu ka?)
items.description:
• THIS MODEL HAS TWO FILES. YOU NEED TO USE THEM TOGETHER!!!
  • The associated trigger words are only for reference, it may need to be adjusted at some times.
  • The recommended weight for the embedding model is 1, which provides higher fidelity; if greater generalization is required, it can be lowered to 0.5.
  • The recommended weight for the LoRA model is 0.85; if there's evidence of contamination, consider lowering it to 0.6.

How to Use This Model

THIS MODEL HAS TWO FILES. YOU NEED TO USE THEM TOGETHER!!!. In this case, you need to download both nygglatho_sukasuka.pt and nygglatho_sukasuka.safetensors, then use nygglatho_sukasuka.pt as texture inversion embedding, and use nygglatho_sukasuka.safetensors as LoRA at the same time.

このモデルには2つのファイルがあります。一緒に使う必要があります！！！。 この場合、nygglatho_sukasuka.ptとnygglatho_sukasuka.safetensorsの両方をダウンロード する必要があります。nygglatho_sukasuka.ptをテクスチャ反転埋め込みとして使用し、同時にnygglatho_sukasuka.safetensorsをLoRAとして使用してください。

这个模型有两个文件。你需要同时使用它们！！！。 在这种情况下，您需要下载nygglatho_sukasuka.pt和nygglatho_sukasuka.safetensors这两个文件，然后将nygglatho_sukasuka.pt用作纹理反转嵌入， 同时使用nygglatho_sukasuka.safetensors作为LoRA。

이 모델은 두 개의 파일이 있습니다. 두 파일을 함께 사용해야 합니다!!!. 이 경우에는 nygglatho_sukasuka.pt와 nygglatho_sukasuka.safetensors 두 파일을 모두 다운로드하신 다음에 nygglatho_sukasuka.pt을 텍스처 반전 임베딩으로 사용하고, 동시에 nygglatho_sukasuka.safetensors을 LoRA로 사용하셔야 합니다.

(Translated with ChatGPT)

The trigger word is nygglatho_sukasuka, and the recommended tags are best quality, masterpiece, highres, solo, {nygglatho_sukasuka:1.15}, long_hair, red_hair, maid_headdress, apron, pink_hair, green_eyes.

How This Model Is Trained

This model is trained with HCP-Diffusion. And the auto-training framework is maintained by DeepGHS Team.

Why Some Preview Images Not Look Like Nygglatho Sukasuka

All the prompt texts used on the preview images (which can be viewed by clicking on the images) are automatically generated using clustering algorithms based on feature information extracted from the training dataset. The seed used during image generation is also randomly generated, and the images have not undergone any selection or modification. As a result, there is a possibility of the mentioned issues occurring.

In practice, based on our internal testing, most models that experience such issues perform better in actual usage than what is seen in the preview images. The only thing you may need to do is adjusting the tags you are using.

I Felt This Model May Be Overfitting or Underfitting, What Shall I Do

Our model has been published on huggingface repository - CyberHarem/nygglatho_sukasuka, where models of all the steps are saved. Also, we published the training dataset on huggingface dataset - CyberHarem/nygglatho_sukasuka, which may be helpful to you.

Why Not Just Using The Better-Selected Images

Our model's entire process, from data crawling, training, to generating preview images and publishing, is 100% automated without any human intervention. It's an interesting experiment conducted by our team, and for this purpose, we have developed a complete set of software infrastructure, including data filtering, automatic training, and automated publishing. Therefore, if possible, we would appreciate more feedback or suggestions as they are highly valuable to us.

Why Can't the Desired Character Outfits Be Accurately Generated

Our current training data is sourced from various image websites, and for a fully automated pipeline, it's challenging to accurately predict which official images a character possesses. Consequently, outfit generation relies on clustering based on labels from the training dataset in an attempt to achieve the best possible recreation. We will continue to address this issue and attempt optimization, but it remains a challenge that cannot be completely resolved. The accuracy of outfit recreation is also unlikely to match the level achieved by manually trained models.

In fact, this model's greatest strengths lie in recreating the inherent characteristics of the characters themselves and its relatively strong generalization capabilities, owing to its larger dataset. As such, this model is well-suited for tasks such as changing outfits, posing characters, and, of course, generating NSFW images of characters!😉".

For the following groups, it is not recommended to use this model and we express regret:

  1. Individuals who cannot tolerate any deviations from the original character design, even in the slightest detail.
  2. Individuals who are facing the application scenarios with high demands for accuracy in recreating character outfits.
  3. Individuals who cannot accept the potential randomness in AI-generated images based on the Stable Diffusion algorithm.
  4. Individuals who are not comfortable with the fully automated process of training character models using LoRA, or those who believe that training character models must be done purely through manual operations to avoid disrespecting the characters.
  5. Individuals who finds the generated image content offensive to their values.

items.name: FoolKat GODDESS-OF-DISCORD
items.description:
It's finally here! This is my first GODDESS series model. The series features 3D semi-realistic and/or 3D cartoon models. The GODDESS-OF-DISCORD model is a semi-realistic model that creates anime styled 3D images.

The model was created by mixing my GOD-OF-ANIME model with MoonRide Mix v10, Goosebumps Cover Art Style (Tim Jacobus style), DarkSun, and AcidBurn.

It has the standard SD 1.5 vae file baked in so no vae is necessary.

All of the images I upload for this model are unedited and don't use any special extensions like ControlNet. I do not do any inpainting or img2img to correct errors. Why? Because you deserve to see how the model works without any touchup or special extensions like ControlNet. You can surely get better images by putting in the extra work, which I do for my personal images. The samples are just meant to showcase what the model can do raw with nothing but prompt engineering.

items.description:
1.0 release

- 3 checkpoints with lora use now integrated one set for each area

- proper explanation of use

- final ui fixes.

V3 - final

3.0 fixes

- improved detection

- proper pasting on most images

- better blending

- added options

- better interface

- better support for lower base sizes

- faster generation

V2.5 working as intended... same thing just working now

Introducing the NSFW generator with HD face and now body enhancing. - This workflow can work some serious magic.

Requires -

https://civitai.com/models/52723/masquerade-nodes-comfyui

https://civitai.com/models/33192/comfyui-impact-pack

and

https://civitai.com/models/20793/wass-comprehensive-node-suite-comfyui

Options not pulled out of nest yet

  • mask to region (constraints and batch behaviour) depending on photo types can improve performance.

Beta 2

Changes - Everything... Big thanks to the adetailer, the masquerade team and the people that make the detection models.

- All faces now fix and enhance automatically. Bodies now do the same

- Can load either a xl or 1.5 model separately for all parts of The main scene, the bodies, and faces

- All changes have their own prompts and all respond really well.

- 100% modular, can bypass any parts you don't want. Just Ctrl bounding box the group and press Ctrl and b

- When doing photos with multiple people, all are enhanced, but each person takes more time. The more complex the photo the more trouble it may have.

- Any resolution is supported, can do some great things with Lower res bases and works quite well with 1.5 base resolutions.

items.name: Kazuma Sketchbook
items.description:
This model is inspired by the color lithographic works of Oda Kazuma from the early 20th century. Unlike his more famous ukiyo-e (woodblock) artwork, his lithographs gave off a much more Western impressionistic artstyle, which makes sense given his studies under an Austrian lithographer.

Keyword:

odkzsb

Negative prompts:

shin-hanga, photograph

Kazuma often drew landscapes and everyday scenes, which is where this model shines. However, it can also do portraits and other things. When making portraits, I usually add photograph as a negative prompt, and/or increase the weight from 1.0 up to 1.25, in order retain the drawn style. Kazuma drew most women in a traditional Japanese style, so Asian women may skew towards that look as well.

Additionally, since his work is quite similar to woodblock printing, adding shin-hanga as a negative prompt is necessary!

All of the source photos came from the NDL public domain gallery on Oda Kazuma, of which you can find some here (it's fun to compare!); However, his monochrome (often sepia toned) lithographs will eventually be adapted into a separate LoRa because they are visually distinct and different from his color lithographs.

Note: Do not use the SDXL Refiner with this LoRa, unless you are okay with it removing the details unique to the artist's style.

modelVersions.name: v0.28
modelVersions.description:
Drastically improved the stylistic resemblance to the source material without overfitting to the source material. Unlike 0.6, which was more abstract, this version aligns far more closely to the intended style. I went through about 22 trainings to get this result.

Style weights and keywords/negative prompts have stayed the same.

items.name: 【再世】next life-笑林
items.description:
这是群星再世第八十九期，以后会不定期出去世的群星Lora，以纪念他们。

经常听相声的人应该对这个名字不会陌生，这里是笑林广播电台，笑林广播电台。

笑林原名赵小林，出生于1956年山东省的一个普通家庭，因为父母都从事文艺事业，笑林在孩童时期便受到了艺术的熏陶，笑林从小就对表演表现出了极高的兴趣和天赋，父母见状便决定将孩子送到专业的学堂进行学习。笑林十分幸运，被当时著名的快书表演艺术家刘司昌看中，成为了他的学徒，在刘司昌的精心教导之下，年仅四岁的笑林便能够自如地登台演出

而当时的笑林不仅在相声表演上有显著的天赋，就连音乐上也表现得十分突出，当时还被选中参加中央广播电台的少年广播合唱团，但到了变声期不符合条件便不在这条路上走下去，笑林当时以小神童出名，稳健的台风，独特的表现风格，细腻的表演细节，都让他在舞台上脱颖而出。年仅五岁的笑林在台上自如地说着快书，已经入行许久的李国盛便看到了这个天赋超群的小男孩，认定他必会出人头地，但是这么也没有想到，他们未来会就这样合作近三十年，那时候的笑林还在年少时期便遇上了董浩（就是大风车的那个董浩叔叔），还成为了后来的一生至交，两人的相遇有些奇妙，当时董浩在笑林的隔壁班，笑林被欺负的时候，董浩就会跑到他们班去为笑林打抱不平董浩曾经回忆那个时候的笑林，他说道：“笑林小时候很乖，后来在文化宫学文艺的时候，还总是被人欺负，而我总是在帮他。”

1979年，李国盛也恰好来到了笑林所在的曲艺团，笑林也没想到在这里他能够遇到自己在事业发展中一生的贵人，也是他最重要的搭档，1980年，李国盛带着自己的新搭档笑林首登相声舞台，虽然李国盛比笑林年长17岁，但两人初登台就十分默契，逗得台下观众哈哈哈大笑，相互抛梗逗趣都十分自然。1986年春晚，两人更是被邀请表演相声《怪声独唱》，这更是令这对有趣的相声搭档走入到千家万户的眼中，那次的舞台之后，他们已经成为了无人不知无人不晓的相声名家，1987年，两人还一起表演了节目《学播音》，从此“笑林广播电台”就正式开播。

2015年，笑林因白血病去世，享年59岁。

https://t.me/+Vm8qxYr2QYgxMjJl 我的群组

ps：素材里有一些笑林年轻时的照片，那时候脸上还没有那个痣。

items.description:
这是群星再世第九十期，以后会不定期出去世的群星Lora，以纪念他们。

侯耀文原名侯跃文，1948年7月17日出生于北京的一个文艺家庭，他父亲名叫侯宝林，是著名的相声大师，曾创作和表演过大量脍炙人口的相声名段，例如《戏剧杂谈》、《夜行记》、《关公战秦琼》等等，桃李满天下的侯宝林还教出了很多优秀的相声演员，其中包括了贾振良、马季、丁广泉、胡必达、师胜杰等大众熟悉的相声名家。因为受到他父亲侯宝林的影响，侯耀华从小就喜欢相声，在他的不断努力下，他很小就打下了扎实的基本功，1960年，12岁的侯耀文第一次登上了舞台，和他父亲侯宝林一起表演了《醉酒》这个相声作品，那时候的侯耀文，一心盼望着快点长大，以后和父亲一样，成为一名受人敬重的相声演员，结果他父亲却要求他好好学习，坚决反对他走相声这一条路。

为了继续说相声，15岁那年，初中刚毕业的侯耀文，瞒着他父亲去参加了铁路文工团的招生考试，想给他父亲来一个先斩后奏，凭借着扎实的基本功，他不仅顺利通过了考试，还在这里遇到了他一生的搭档石富宽，而他父亲在得知他已经考上文工团后，也只能无奈同意了，进入文工团后，侯耀文跟随单位的同事到处演出，短短的几年时间里就创作出了《智勇双全》、《小球推着大球转》等十几个相声段子。1976年，他和搭档石富宽接连推出了《财迷丈人》、《见义勇为》、《戏曲漫谈》等相声作品，凭借着这些优秀的作品，以及在舞台上的出色表演，他们迅速火了起来。1983年，在第一届央视春晚举办的时候，35岁的侯耀文受邀登上了央视春晚的舞台，和石富宽一起表演了《讲礼貌》这个作品，自此他才家喻户晓。

1984年春晚《糖醋鲤鱼》，1988春晚主持人，1989年和赵丽蓉奶奶一起演出《英雄母亲的一天》，1994年春晚和黄宏一起演出《打扑克》……

2004年，侯耀文收徒郭德纲

2007年，侯耀文因心脏病突发去世，享年59岁。

2011年才被下葬，在去世之后的这四年里，侯耀文的大女儿侯瓒和侯耀文的二哥侯耀华，因为遗产的分配问题意见不一致，两人彻底闹掰，一边指责对方搬空父亲的遗产，另一边则对于这样的控诉毫不理会，但最终，双方谈妥了。

唉，一地鸡毛。

items.name: EZero
items.description:
EZero is a custom merge that I made because why not.

It probably isn't great at fine details or NSFW, but I haven't tested the latter, so please do test it for me. Thanks.

One workaround for the details part is to do 1.5x 0.6 denoise img2img at low CFG (3 or 4).

Use it however you want, except selling the model itself.

Good settings for this model

CFG - 3~7

Resolution - 640x640 and higher

Sampler - Restart, UniPC, DPM++ 3M SDE Exponential

Restart is the best sampler for this IMO. CFG 7 with 12 steps.

UniPC is a very fast and weird sampler. It seems to converge at Step count = 2x CFG, which is pretty neat. CFG 3 with 6 steps is good.

DPM++ 3M SDE Exponential just give it very low CFG (2~3) and high step count (16).
